01:34:49,385 --> 01:34:52,053
Wait a minute,
we're not just gonna
let these criminals go, right?

2224
01:34:52,055 --> 01:34:53,688
Ah, come on, commish.
Let's face it.

2225
01:34:53,690 --> 01:34:55,856
Those guys are no match
for the four of us.

2226
01:34:55,858 --> 01:34:57,692
We'll give them
a 30-minute head start.

2227
01:34:57,694 --> 01:35:00,494
Besides, you can't fight crime
on an empty stomach.

2228
01:35:03,231 --> 01:35:04,632
Hey, computer?

2229
01:35:04,634 --> 01:35:05,966
We're home!

2230
01:35:09,504 --> 01:35:10,805
<i> What is the password?</i>

2231
01:35:10,807 --> 01:35:12,540
Iron man sucks!

2232
01:35:24,553 --> 01:35:25,753
When dad
and me were fighting,

2233
01:35:25,755 --> 01:35:27,488
I was giving them
my best one-liners.

2234
01:35:28,223 --> 01:35:29,290
<i> You</i>

2235
01:35:31,393 --> 01:35:33,094
<i> complete me.</i>

2236
01:35:46,341 --> 01:35:49,443
Holy family photo, Batman.
I love it!

2237
01:35:56,351 --> 01:35:57,752
<i> White.</i>

2238
01:35:57,754 --> 01:36:02,356
<i> All important movies end</i>
<i> with a white screen.</i>

2239
01:36:02,358 --> 01:36:04,592
<i> And tying up loose ends.</i>

2240
01:36:04,594 --> 01:36:06,861
We're coming for you,
Gotham city!

2241
01:36:06,863 --> 01:36:08,395
<i> Like </i>
<i> this snake clowns bit.</i>

2242
01:36:08,397 --> 01:36:09,630
<i> Snake clowns?</i>

2243
01:36:09,632 --> 01:36:11,298
<i> Told you </i>
<i> they were real.</i>

2244
01:36:11,300 --> 01:36:13,033
<i> Did you stick wigs </i>
<i> onto snakes?</i>

2245
01:36:13,035 --> 01:36:15,069
<i>- Maybe.</i>
<i>- That is so weird.</i>

2246
01:36:15,071 --> 01:36:16,637
<i> Can I play that song </i>
<i> I wrote for the end credits?</i>

2247
01:36:16,639 --> 01:36:17,905
<i> That is a hard pass.</i>

2248
01:36:17,907 --> 01:36:19,774
<i>- Come on.</i>
<i>- No!</i>

2249
01:36:19,776 --> 01:36:21,208
<i> Let the kid play </i>
<i> whatever music he wants.</i>

2250
01:36:21,210 --> 01:36:22,443
<i>- No, no, no!</i>
<i>- Please?</i>

2251
01:36:22,445 --> 01:36:23,611
<i>- No.</i>
- Padre?

2252
01:36:23,613 --> 01:36:25,379
<i> Fine. 'Puter.</i>

2253
01:36:25,381 --> 01:36:26,714
<i> Okay, sir.</i>

2254
01:36:26,716 --> 01:36:28,649
<i> Yay!</i>

2255
01:36:28,651 --> 01:36:30,618
<i> Now playing </i>
<i> Robin's happy, poppy music.</i>

2256
01:36:30,620 --> 01:36:33,954
<i> The kind that makes parents</i>
<i> and studio executives happy.</i>

2257
01:36:57,646 --> 01:36:58,712
Come on, everyone!

2258
01:37:18,266 --> 01:37:19,667
Come on, Batman!
No!

2259
01:38:46,888 --> 01:38:49,523
Wow, that was fun!

2260
01:38:49,525 --> 01:38:52,059
Really hope
nobody was recording that.

2261
01:38:52,061 --> 01:38:53,627
Let me see.
Oh, this thing is on.

2262
01:38:53,629 --> 01:38:54,628
This thing is recording.
